####INSTALL
NODE(LINUX): sudo apt-get install nodejs

npm install - typescript

For check:
node -v
npm -v
tsc -v

####CONFIG
tsc --init

Create two paste (in this exemple):
BUILD >>> outDir
SRC >>> rootDir

Uncomment and insert name paste in tsconfig.json
// "outDir": "./",
// "rootDir": "./"   

####BUILD
tsc --watch SRC rootDir
node NAMEFILE BUILD rootDir